1. A well-crafted vision statement can help a change-leading organization by:
solution : A. Inspiring the workforce to create the future

2. In addition to creating transformative innovations, what other innovation activities do change-leading organizations focus on?
solution : D. Executing incremental improvements that help customers and lead to big gains

3. If you scored your organization poorly in an area on the diagnostic tool, you should:
solution : C. Sit down with your manager to discuss it and to find out more
